tuitive, flowy controls\n- Collecting fish of different colors", "short_description": "Tiny Fins lets you swim free in an ocean playground, guiding a school of cute fish with a sweep of your hand. Dive past colorful clams, snag bunches of bubbles, and avoid hungry sharks!\n\nWhy you will love it: Super-smooth controls that make sudden sprints and quick pivots a cinch when you\u2019re gliding through the water. They\u2019re a lifesaver when you go from popping a string of bubbles to deftly avoiding a spiky puffer fish!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://tiny-fins.com/imprint.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Ditached GmbH", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://ditached.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "de", "fr", "fr_CA", "ja", "zh_CN", "zh_HK", "zh_TW"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "26652350321030138"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 3, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2046530205764406"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1319438632776054"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "559210789767808"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "559210789767808"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1725987600, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "559210789767808"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results"